sub_title: Founder of Bulgarian Achievers - Intercultural coaching & consulting
summary:
If you are a Bulgarian who lives/studies/works abroad or an expat located in Bulgaria and you want to build positive experience and thrive in the new cultural environment - Bulgarian Achievers is here for you! 

The services may vary according to your particular needs. However, there are a few things that won’t change during our time together – personal approach, engagement, encouragement, etc. 

Now, tell me more about you!
